{"tid":99220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文]大撚獲 一陣班親戚黎拜年","createTime":"2017-01-29T04:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T08:55:10.000Z","uid":21731,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24e83aba9ea13e3ce453966c04b9a62274cb48e2","tid":99220,"uid":21731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"唉，宜家都唔知點算......<br />\n<br />\n話說我今年考DSE，前幾日放榜，<br />\n但考得麻麻，但係又怕呀媽擔心，<br />\n老母一生人既夢想就係見到個仔入大學。<br />\n因為d親戚街坊都無人入到大學。<br />\n<br />\n今日一早返左屋企時，<br />\n呀媽係咁問我成績點，夠唔夠分, 可以入邊間大學，<br />\n但係我心情唔好，<br />\n求其同呀媽講「入左hku space engineering」<br />\n之後就入左房訓覺。(因為尋晚通左頂)<br />\n<br />\n跟住我起左身，屙完屎之後出黎 ⋯⋯<br />\n發現成家人都好撚開心，<br />\n呀爸呀媽叫撚晒d親戚姑姐姨媽話今晚出黎食飯拜年<br />\n同我慶祝入到HKU讀宇宙工程。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候先知道大撚鑊，<br />\n我其實係去報港大太空學院，<br />\n唔撚知邊個親戚街坊話係港大，<br />\n只有HKU有space engine讀，<br />\n所以呀媽以為我夠分入左HKU，<br />\n仲同我講第時畢業可以入N.A.S.A.(美國太空總署)整太空船，<br />\n人工仲高過MBBS同GBUS果d垃圾科。<br />\n等陣成班親戚來食飯恭喜佢入港大。<br />\n<br />\n呢隻鑊都唔知點收科........."},{"pid":"25ac588db5965b877df9f8a336366022c24bbe9b","tid":99220,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:39:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ac479ef9b037942ad08834a8a0bc201e79d4452","tid":99220,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前幾日放榜<br />\n樓主咩時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依加樓豬只係殘影黎，實體應該係2018<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓豬用光速運行緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1624aa59d34f5d33d2e1e7a56cf26320d384f2f7","tid":99220,"uid":46649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"咁多真心?"},{"pid":"f63f0b56a5b70f34bb1435a5f9ea3982b617b979","tid":99220,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:49:58.000Z","msg":"尾2果句改漏左個「佢」字，下次努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f6c760e5f2b86543073dab569163e8d3afea7a","tid":99220,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:59:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ef42125dc04418ecf174dc51a0a3f6de8c3665b","tid":99220,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:24:40.000Z","msg":"啲仆街一年見一次，前年拜年我仲係fg廢青，<br />\n羞辱我冇用揾唔到工<br />\n事隔兩年，今年黎到問我幾錢人工<br />\n&quot;三萬鬆啲，之前由未揾到工到而家咁快就兩年啦&quot;<br />\n當我答完三萬鬆啲即刻收皮"},{"pid":"4bee2c0a1e55e671e7d3622ab0dc2d11d9424671","tid":99220,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:26:27.000Z","msg":"我會出街，如果有錢，不如出國去旅行"},{"pid":"add06558f9a5a4f997c4eee33e350670bab39d17","tid":99220,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:29:36.000Z","msg":"知唔撚知乜尻野叫長文"},{"pid":"dc87d564678536b7b549c4d52bb178c3836b9ee2","tid":99220,"uid":33655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"好多新會然"},{"pid":"7fcd79d5d9dd88ee9d708957dbb73a5f833af8a1","tid":99220,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:55:10.000Z","msg":"我都唔撚想去你屋企拜年，老豆老母迫我去有乜辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}